  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function glib_renderer_source_new(renderer: <link xref="Cogl.Renderer">Cogl.Renderer</link>, priority: Number(gint)): <link href="../GLib-2.0/GLib.Source.html">GLib.Source</link> {
    // Gjs wrapper for cogl_glib_renderer_source_new()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Creates a <link href="../GLib-2.0/GLib.Source.html">GLib.Source</link> which handles Cogl's internal system event
processing. This can be used as a convenience instead of
<link xref="Cogl.poll_renderer_get_info"/> and <link xref="Cogl.poll_renderer_dispatch"/> in
applications that are already using the GLib main loop. After this
is called the <link href="../GLib-2.0/GLib.Source.html">GLib.Source</link> should be attached to the main loop using
g_source_attach().</p>
  <p>Since 1.16</p>
